acqinfo.p: The collection was received via administrative transfers from the Humanities Honors Program. Additional theses were transferred from the Hume Writing Center in 2011.

accessrestrict.head: Information about Access
accessrestrict.p: Collection is open for research; materials must be requested at least 24 hours in advance of intended use. No photocopies may be made.

userestrict.head: Ownership & Copyright
userestrict.p: Copyright is retained by the creators for materials they have authored or otherwise produced. Transmission or reproduction of materials requires the written permission of the copyright owner.
